"```sql\nSELECT c.name, st.language\nFROM cards c\nJOIN set_translations st ON c.setCode = st.setCode\nWHERE c.setCode = '10E' AND c.convertedManaCost = 5;\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the names of cards and their translation languages from the set with the code '10E' that have a converted mana cost of 5. It joins the `cards` table with the `set_translations` table using the `setCode` to find the relevant translations."